      "text": "My name is Peter Bowman and I am a 19-year-old student at Cal Poly San Luis Obispo pursuing a dual degree in Mathematics and Computer Science. I am deeply passionate about exploring the intersection of these two fields and am actively engaged in projects that allow me to push the boundaries of what is possible. My work often involves complex problem-solving, innovative thinking, and a relentless drive to create something meaningful. I am also an avid photographer, finding inspiration in capturing the world around me."
